    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Quick Start</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">The fastest path from a built binary to an interactive SRM prompt, and back down cleanly. Each step has its own topic below; follow them in order.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">In this section</para>
    <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="NotesBox" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="NotesBox">Launching EmulatR -- start the emulator from the Emulatr root.</li>
      <li styleclass="NotesBox">Connecting to the Console -- attach a terminal to the TCP console.</li>
      <li styleclass="NotesBox">Loading Firmware -- point the run at the SRM image.</li>
      <li styleclass="NotesBox">Reaching the SRM Prompt -- what the power-up sequence shows.</li>
      <li styleclass="NotesBox">Clean Shutdown -- stop the emulator so NVRAM is flushed.</li>
    </list>
